verbose_text: Addition of wild-type hAha1, comprised of phospho- and non phosphorylated Y223, stimulated ATPase activity of the hHsp90alpha 5-fold higher than that of hHsp90alpha, alone, while hAha1-Y223F caused minimal increase in ATPase activity (1.5-fold increase) (XREF_FIG and S4E).
evidence: wild-type hAha1, comprised of phospho- and non-phosphorylated Y223, stimulated ATPase
